#Text=WATERLOO IRON FOUNDRY AND AGRICULTURAL IMPLEMENT M.\\ NUFACTORY, NEAR POOLE, DORSET, BEG to inform their numerous Friends and the Public, that they will Exhibit at the forthcoming SHOW, in SHED No. 15.
